		Vestibulum condimentum  facilisis nulla. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nulla nonummy. Cras quis libero.</p>
}
else
{
	<p>There are no events planned at the moment</p>
}
	</section>

   <section class="group5">
   <h3>Past events</h3>
@if (Model.PastEvents != null && Model.PastEvents.Count > 0)
{
    foreach (var e in Model.PastEvents)
    {
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Event", new { id = e.Id, slug = e.Slug })"><h4>@e.Title</h4></a>
        <p>@Html.Html5EventDateTimeTag(e.StartsAt, e.EndsAt)</p>
		<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Donec molestie. Sed aliquam sem ut arcu. Phasellus sollicitudin. 
		Vestibulum condimentum  facilisis nulla. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nulla nonummy. Cras quis libero.</p>
    }
}
else
{
	<p>No events to show</p>
}
	</section>
    </div>